Check Stan

check_cmdstanr.Rd

Check whether cmdstanr is available and prints version and logistic example.

Usage

check_cmdstanr()

Examples

check_cmdstanr()
#> cmdstan version: 
#> [1] "2.30.1"
#> Example program:
#> data {
#>   int<lower=0> N;
#>   int<lower=0> K;

#>   matrix[N, K] X;
#> }
#> parameters {
#>   real alpha;

#> model {
#>   target += normal_lpdf(alpha | 0, 1);
#>   target += normal_lpdf(beta | 0, 1);
#>   target += bernoulli_logit_glm_lpmf(y | X, alpha, beta);
